rismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xot1665702631323.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xot1665702631323.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xot1665702631323.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xot1665702631323\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether an ellipsis (<code class=\"ph codeph\">…</code>) is displayed when there is more data than fits in a text field and the field does not have focus. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xot1665702631323__section_uff_4pk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d946728e59\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xot1665702631323__table_d12191e1_d12192e1_d12193e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xot1665702631323__section_i45_ppk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d946728e105\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"xot1665702631323__note_mh4_rpk_zwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If a field is defined with the field syntax set to NDI\n        (no display), the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Show Ellipsis</span> is turned off.</div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"xot1665702631323__fig_d107069e1_d107070e1_d107071e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Show Ellipsis in Mobile Application</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Show Ellipsis in Mobile Application example\" class=\"image\" id=\"xot1665702631323__image_glt_spk_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/showellipsis.gif?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xot1665702631323__section_qdm_tpk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d946728e129\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xot1665702631323__ul_a5j_vpk_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xot1665702631323__li_d42209e1_d42210e1_d42211e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vmo1688449724415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmo1688449724415.html\" title=\"The ucombobox widget combines an input field with a drop-down list. It allows users to select one item from a previously defined list, or enter their own data instead. It is applicable only to form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ComboBox, which is mapped to ucombobox.\">ucombobox (Combo Box)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xot1665702631323__li_d42212e1_d42213e1_d42214e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617001\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617001\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Show Ellipsis Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether an ellipsis ( … ) is displayed when there is more data than fits in a text field and the field does not have focus. True or False (default). Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description Note: If a field is defined with the field syntax set to NDI (no display), the Show Ellipsis is turned off. Figure 1. Show Ellipsis in Mobile Application Applies to ucombobox (Combo Box) EditBox Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}